@startuml seq-09-search
' 序列图9：全局搜索(5表UNION ALL)
title 全局搜索序列图（5表 UNION ALL）

actor 用户 as User
participant "global-search.js" as Front
participant "SearchController" as Ctrl
participant "SearchService" as Svc
participant "SearchMapper.xml" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 输入关键词"榫卯"
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/search/global?keyword=榫卯&limit=20
Ctrl -> Svc: search(keyword,limit)
Svc -> Mapper: search(keyword,limit)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT 'article' AS type,... FROM article WHERE title LIKE '%榫卯%' UNION ALL SELECT 'user_work'... UNION ALL SELECT 'course'... UNION ALL SELECT 'post'... UNION ALL SELECT 'article'...(结构类) LIMIT 20
DB --> Mapper: 聚合结果集
Mapper --> Svc: List<Map>
Svc -> Svc: 按type分组
Svc --> Ctrl: List<SearchResultVO>
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:List}
Front -> Front: 分组渲染(文章/作品/课程/帖子)
Front --> User: 显示搜索结果

@enduml
